Me:  I love being a wizzy<br>
He:  Yah, Wizzy has their uses.<br>
Me:  Listen to this guy, wizzy has their uses.  Wizzy rules.  We uber-class.<br>
He:  All u do is nuke.<br>
Me:  And its enuff.  Not like u pet classes.  Kill the mob yourself why dont u.<br>
He:  U must be thinking about Mages, Necro no need pet.<br>
Me:  Yah, mages suck.  Screw 'em.<br>
He:  Yah, screw 'em.<br>
<br>
See, the word is getting out there.  Mages = screw 'em  P<br>
